data.meta_description: Cr Manufacturer - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides an index of abbreviated manufacturer names used in a cross reference list. It contains over 200 abbreviations for manufacturer names and the corresponding full names. The abbreviations are used to identify part numbers from different manufacturers to allow for cross referencing. Users should verify the manufacturer name when using the cross reference to ensure accuracy.
